#: ../../source/Chapter4.rst:895
# 189e0c1972a0401daeff347be3846f2a
msgid "A VFD was installed and the supply fan was operated at 80% of full speed for eight days from February 11-19, 2001. The system was then controlled to maintain a constant static pressure set point (0.7 in. H2O) from February 19-27, 2001."
