msgid "Figure 4-20 compares the measured hourly supply fan power for the constant speed and constant static pressure operation. The average fan power was reduced from 35.8 kW for the CSFS operation to 23.1 kW for the VSFS operation. The average fan power savings of 12.7 kW corresponds to a 35% reduction in fan power. More details may be found in Joo et al. [2002]."
